<paragraph id="08EB0346ADF075C546D23B159DE6E284" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6F539369BDC69E7960A0F9B2BC9E31" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">
<emphasis id="C55E76684F543C9ABC8C20D9BC58A857" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">Mycelium</emphasis>
superficial and immersed composed of septate, smooth-walled, hyaline hyphae, 2.5-5.5 
<normalizedToken id="33B0DA604452247B3204B8EA8E2FC91E" originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
wide. 
<emphasis id="B032C6F343A90469DBF1BAD06ACF165C" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">Conidiophores</emphasis>
biverticillate, terverticillate or quaterverticillate; 
<emphasis id="F98D35AEA8B47BA81AD827F189A43E44" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">stipes</emphasis>
smooth-walled, 40-200 
<normalizedToken id="F033C2D568D2AE85D4DF7669AB850F50" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
2.5-4 
<normalizedToken id="B4AC644E8CD6446076ABD488F6EECDB8" originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
; 
<emphasis id="8944C96872E5BADE50AF78CA57C4904A" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">metulae</emphasis>
appressed to slightly divergent, 2-4 per branch or stipe, vesiculate, 6-12.5 
<normalizedToken id="F2775ACC2F30C4BA7715C15BD613D888" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
2-4 
<normalizedToken id="985B5244BB1AA7142F11937774811347" originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
(vesicle up to 4.5 
<normalizedToken id="80CF302CDE72321E456DCA9862EE5091" originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
wide); 
<emphasis id="839C3CF1BE71B70DE4C9AF6353A9E9D0" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">phialides</emphasis>
3-6 per metulae, ampulliform, 5.5-7.5 
<normalizedToken id="5BDB616D3E48223BFC7D7DF66C0A47E4" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
1.5-2.5 
<normalizedToken id="BF237FA0DA306CBEEBA7A0E144624C9C" originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
; 
<emphasis id="D27CA3ABD56D5ECE634ACB029DA4C5F2" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">conidia</emphasis>
smooth-walled, globose to subglobose, 2.5-3 
<normalizedToken id="F91125E34B13139E6DCCFF7E1B34EC86" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
2.5-3 
<normalizedToken id="3E2DDAA92E61ECB96BD076CD3A363FC6" originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<caption id="D71C1A5014A63B6B90B7839B25BB7B4B" doi="10.3897/mycokeys.86.73861.figure15" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/640614" pageId="0" pageNumber="103" start="Figure 15" startId="F15">
