Swamp, from sediments, Feb 2018, 
<emphasis id="343926A13ACA4BE7F3DC8F728B0912FF" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">E. Carvalho</emphasis>
&amp; 
<emphasis id="401043BC53A8C7464855B2D8E98D0E77" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">
